<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>VIP Technologies — Event Intelligence Platform</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
  --red:      #e01c1c;
  --red-glow: rgba(224,28,28,0.35);
  --red-dim:  rgba(224,28,28,0.12);
  --white:    #f0eeea;
  --dim:      rgba(240,238,234,0.45);
  --dimmer:   rgba(240,238,234,0.18);
  --black:    #060608;
  --panel:    rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
  --border:   rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--black);
  color: var(--white);
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  min-height: 100vh;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── Animated grid background ── */
.grid-bg {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.022) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.022) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  animation: gridshift 25s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes gridshift {
  from { background-position: 0 0, 0 0; }
  to   { background-position: 60px 60px, 60px 60px; }
}

/* ── Red horizon glow ── */
.horizon {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: -10%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 140vw;
  height: 60vh;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center bottom,
    rgba(224,28,28,0.18) 0%,
    rgba(224,28,28,0.06) 30%,
    transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

.top-glow {
  position: fixed;
  top: -20%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 80vw;
  height: 50vh;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center,
    rgba(200,200,255,0.04) 0%,
    transparent 60%);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

/* ── Scan line ── */
.scanline {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right,
    transparent 0%, rgba(224,28,28,0.6) 50%, transparent 100%);
  animation: scan 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  z-index: 5;
  pointer-events: none;
}

@keyframes scan {
  0%   { top: 0%; opacity: 0; }
  5%   { opacity: 1; }
  95%  { opacity: 0.4; }
  100% { top: 100%; opacity: 0; }
}

/* ── Wrapper ── */
.wrapper {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 10;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
  text-align: center;
}

/* ── System label ── */
.sys-label {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--red);
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 0.8s ease 0.3s forwards;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}

.sys-label::before, .sys-label::after {
  content: '';
  display: block;
  width: 40px;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--red));
}

.sys-label::after {
  background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, var(--red));
}

/* ── LOGO ── */
.logo-wrap {
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 1s ease 0.5s forwards;
}

/* Hexagon SVG logo */
.hex-logo {
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
}

.hex-logo svg {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  overflow: visible;
}

/* Rotating outer ring */
.ring-outer {
  animation: rotatering 20s linear infinite;
  transform-origin: center;
}

.ring-inner {
  animation: rotatering 12s linear infinite reverse;
  transform-origin: center;
}

@keyframes rotatering {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

/* Pulse on center mark */
.center-pulse {
  animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  transform-origin: center;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; r: 4; }
  50%       { opacity: 0.4; r: 6; }
}

/* VIP text glow flicker */
.vip-text {
  animation: textflicker 8s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes textflicker {
  0%, 96%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  97%            { opacity: 0.85; }
  98%            { opacity: 1; }
  99%            { opacity: 0.9; }
}

/* ── Company name ── */
.company-name {
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 1s ease 0.9s forwards;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.name-vector {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--white);
}

.name-vector .highlight { color: var(--red); }

.name-sub {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(11px, 2vw, 15px);
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.35em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--dimmer);
  margin-top: 8px;
}

/* ── Divider ── */
.tech-divider {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  margin: 2.75rem auto;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 600px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 1s ease 1.1s forwards;
}

.td-line {
  flex: 1;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(to right,
    transparent, rgba(224,28,28,0.5), rgba(255,255,255,0.15), rgba(224,28,28,0.5), transparent);
}

.td-nodes {
  display: flex;
  gap: 5px;
  align-items: center;
}

.td-node {
  width: 4px; height: 4px;
  background: var(--red);
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--red-glow);
}

.td-node.big {
  width: 7px; height: 7px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--red-glow);
}

/* ── Hero statement ── */
.hero-statement {
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 1s ease 1.2s forwards;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.hero-line1 {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(11px, 2.2vw, 14px);
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--red);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.hero-line2 {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(18px, 4vw, 30px);
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--dim);
  line-height: 1.5;
  max-width: 640px;
}

.hero-line2 strong {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--white);
}

/* ── Capability grid ── */
.cap-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
  gap: 1px;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 2.5rem auto;
  background: var(--border);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 1s ease 1.4s forwards;
}

.cap-cell {
  background: var(--black);
  padding: 18px 16px;
  text-align: left;
  transition: background 0.3s ease;
  cursor: default;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.cap-cell::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0;
  width: 2px; height: 0;
  background: var(--red);
  transition: height 0.3s ease;
}

.cap-cell:hover { background: rgba(224,28,28,0.04); }
.cap-cell:hover::before { height: 100%; }

.cap-icon {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--red);
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  display: block;
}

.cap-title {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1.3;
}

/* ── Intelligence callout ── */
.intel-callout {
  border: 1px solid rgba(224,28,28,0.25);
  background: var(--red-dim);
  padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
  max-width: 620px;
  width: 100%;
  margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  position: relative;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 1s ease 1.6s forwards;
}

.intel-callout::before, .intel-callout::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 12px; height: 12px;
  border-color: var(--red);
  border-style: solid;
}

.intel-callout::before {
  top: -1px; left: -1px;
  border-width: 2px 0 0 2px;
}

.intel-callout::after {
  bottom: -1px; right: -1px;
  border-width: 0 2px 2px 0;
}

.intel-label {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--red);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.intel-text {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 17px);
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--dim);
  line-height: 1.65;
}

.intel-text strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 600; }

/* ── Contact ── */
.contact-wrap {
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 1s ease 1.8s forwards;
  text-align: center;
}

.contact-label {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.28em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--dimmer);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.phone {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 9vw, 70px);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  color: var(--white);
  text-decoration: none;
  display: block;
  line-height: 1;
  transition: color 0.3s, text-shadow 0.3s;
  text-shadow: 0 0 0 transparent;
}

.phone:hover {
  color: var(--red);
  text-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--red-glow);
}

.phone-note {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--dimmer);
  margin-top: 10px;
}

/* ── Footer ── */
.footer-mark {
  margin-top: 4rem;
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(240,238,234,0.1);
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadein 1s ease 2s forwards;
}

/* ── Animations ── */
@keyframes fadein {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(14px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* ── Mobile ── */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .hex-logo { width: 150px; height: 150px; }
  .cap-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .intel-callout { padding: 1.25rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="grid-bg"></div>
<div class="horizon"></div>
<div class="top-glow"></div>
<div class="scanline"></div>

<div class="wrapper">

  <!-- System label -->
  <div class="sys-label">VIP // SYSTEM ONLINE // ORLANDO FL</div>

  <!-- SVG Logo -->
  <div class="logo-wrap">
    <div class="hex-logo">
      <svg viewBox="-110 -110 220 220" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <filter id="redglow">
            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="blur"/>
            <feMerge><feMergeNode in="blur"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge>
          </filter>
          <filter id="softglow">
            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="6" result="blur"/>
            <feMerge><feMergeNode in="blur"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge>
          </filter>
        </defs>

        <!-- Outer dashed rotating ring -->
        <g class="ring-outer">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="98"
            fill="none" stroke="rgba(224,28,28,0.3)" stroke-width="0.5"
            stroke-dasharray="4 8"/>
          <!-- Tick marks -->
          <line x1="0" y1="-92" x2="0" y2="-102" stroke="#e01c1c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6"/>
          <line x1="0" y1="-92" x2="0" y2="-102" stroke="#e01c1c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6" transform="rotate(45)"/>
          <line x1="0" y1="-92" x2="0" y2="-102" stroke="#e01c1c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6" transform="rotate(90)"/>
          <line x1="0" y1="-92" x2="0" y2="-102" stroke="#e01c1c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6" transform="rotate(135)"/>
          <line x1="0" y1="-92" x2="0" y2="-102" stroke="#e01c1c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6" transform="rotate(180)"/>
          <line x1="0" y1="-92" x2="0" y2="-102" stroke="#e01c1c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6" transform="rotate(225)"/>
          <line x1="0" y1="-92" x2="0" y2="-102" stroke="#e01c1c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6" transform="rotate(270)"/>
          <line x1="0" y1="-92" x2="0" y2="-102" stroke="#e01c1c" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6" transform="rotate(315)"/>
          <!-- Corner diamonds -->
          <rect x="-4" y="-101" width="8" height="8" fill="#e01c1c"
            transform="rotate(45 0 -97)" filter="url(#redglow)" opacity="0.9"/>
          <rect x="-4" y="-101" width="8" height="8" fill="#e01c1c"
            transform="rotate(45 0 -97) rotate(90)" opacity="0.6"/>
          <rect x="-4" y="-101" width="8" height="8" fill="#e01c1c"
            transform="rotate(45 0 -97) rotate(180)" opacity="0.6"/>
          <rect x="-4" y="-101" width="8" height="8" fill="#e01c1c"
            transform="rotate(45 0 -97) rotate(270)" opacity="0.6"/>
        </g>

        <!-- Inner counter-rotating ring with segments -->
        <g class="ring-inner">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="76"
            fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.07)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="76"
            fill="none" stroke="rgba(224,28,28,0.5)" stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-dasharray="24 12" stroke-dashoffset="0"/>
        </g>

        <!-- Hexagon body -->
        <polygon
          points="0,-68 58.9,-34 58.9,34 0,68 -58.9,34 -58.9,-34"
          fill="rgba(6,6,8,0.95)"
          stroke="#e01c1c"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          filter="url(#softglow)"/>

        <!-- Inner hex hairline -->
        <polygon
          points="0,-56 48.5,-28 48.5,28 0,56 -48.5,28 -48.5,-28"
          fill="none"
          stroke="rgba(224,28,28,0.2)"
          stroke-width="0.5"/>

        <!-- Hex corner accent marks -->
        <circle cx="0"     cy="-68"  r="2.5" fill="#e01c1c" filter="url(#redglow)"/>
        <circle cx="58.9"  cy="-34"  r="2.5" fill="#e01c1c" filter="url(#redglow)"/>
        <circle cx="58.9"  cy="34"   r="2.5" fill="#e01c1c" filter="url(#redglow)"/>
        <circle cx="0"     cy="68"   r="2.5" fill="#e01c1c" filter="url(#redglow)"/>
        <circle cx="-58.9" cy="34"   r="2.5" fill="#e01c1c" filter="url(#redglow)"/>
        <circle cx="-58.9" cy="-34"  r="2.5" fill="#e01c1c" filter="url(#redglow)"/>

        <!-- Crosshair lines inside hex -->
        <line x1="-48" y1="0" x2="48" y2="0"
          stroke="rgba(224,28,28,0.15)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
        <line x1="0" y1="-48" x2="0" y2="48"
          stroke="rgba(224,28,28,0.15)" stroke-width="0.5"/>

        <!-- V.I.P letters -->
        <g class="vip-text" filter="url(#redglow)">
          <text x="0" y="14"
            text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Orbitron, sans-serif"
            font-size="38"
            font-weight="900"
            fill="white"
            letter-spacing="6">
            VIP
          </text>
        </g>

        <!-- Center pulse dot -->
        <circle class="center-pulse" cx="0" cy="0" r="3"
          fill="#e01c1c" filter="url(#redglow)"/>

      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Company name -->
  <div class="company-name">
    <div class="name-vector">
      <span class="highlight">V</span>ector&nbsp;
      <span class="highlight">I</span>ntegrated&nbsp;
      <span class="highlight">P</span>roduction
    </div>
    <div class="name-sub">Technologies &nbsp;·&nbsp; Event Intelligence Platform</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="tech-divider">
    <div class="td-line"></div>
    <div class="td-nodes">
      <div class="td-node"></div>
      <div class="td-node big"></div>
      <div class="td-node"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="td-line"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero statement -->
  <div class="hero-statement">
    <div class="hero-line1">The Future of Event Production</div>
    <div class="hero-line2">
      <strong>Real-time intelligence.</strong> Precision labor. Seamless execution.<br>
      We don't just run events — we engineer them.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Capabilities grid -->
  <div class="cap-grid">
    <div class="cap-cell">
      <span class="cap-icon">// 01</span>
      <div class="cap-title">Event Intelligence</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cap-cell">
      <span class="cap-icon">// 02</span>
      <div class="cap-title">Real-Time Labor Tracking</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cap-cell">
      <span class="cap-icon">// 03</span>
      <div class="cap-title">Audio &amp; Video Systems</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cap-cell">
      <span class="cap-icon">// 04</span>
      <div class="cap-title">Lighting &amp; Staging</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cap-cell">
      <span class="cap-icon">// 05</span>
      <div class="cap-title">Technical Direction</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cap-cell">
      <span class="cap-icon">// 06</span>
      <div class="cap-title">Data-Driven Production</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Intelligence callout -->
  <div class="intel-callout">
    <div class="intel-label">// Event Intelligence — Active</div>
    <div class="intel-text">
      VIP Technologies is pioneering the next generation of live event infrastructure —
      combining <strong>NFC-enabled crew management</strong>, <strong>AI-assisted decision making</strong>,
      and <strong>real-time production analytics</strong> into a single unified platform.
      Built for meeting planners and production companies who demand more than execution —
      they demand <strong>intelligence</strong>.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <div class="contact-wrap">
    <div class="contact-label">// Connect with us</div>
    <a class="phone" href="tel:+14049228608">(404) 922-8608</a>
    <div class="phone-note">Orlando, FL &nbsp;·&nbsp; Available for Inquiries &amp; Bookings</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer-mark">
    © Vector Integrated Production Technologies &nbsp;·&nbsp; vip-tech.io &nbsp;·&nbsp; All Rights Reserved
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
